This paper deals with knowledge graphs and link prediction, which are topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves the use of embeddings and distance functions, which are common in database (cs.DB) and natural language processing (cs.CL) research. Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on benchmark datasets, which is a common practice in information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
